OL,3,CMother pleads guilty to killing her
OL,4,Cdaughter, 10, in Rowley Regis
OL,6,FA mother has pleaded guilty to killing
OL,7,Fher 10-year-old daughter.
OL,9,FJaskirat Kaur admitted the
OL,10,Fmanslaughter of Shay Kang on the basis
OL,11,Fof diminished responsibility at
OL,12,FWolverhampton Crown Court on Friday.
OL,14,FShay was found dead in Robin Close,
OL,15,FRowley Regis, West Midlands, after
OL,16,Fpolice were called to her home at
OL,17,Fabout 12.10pm on Monday March 4.
