OL,6,FBrickhouse Primary School pupil Shay
OL,7,Fdied as a result of stab wounds to the
OL,8,Fchest, the opening of an inquest at
OL,9,FBlack Country Coroner's Court heard in
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FKaur, 33, denied murdering her
OL,13,Fdaughter but prosecution counsel Sally
OL,14,FHowes KC said her guilty plea to
OL,15,Fmanslaughter was acceptable to the
OL,16,FCrown.
OL,18,FDefence barrister Katherine Goddard KC
OL,19,Fsaid there was "no dispute over the
OL,20,Ffacts" of the case.
