OL,3,CMother pleads guilty to killing her
OL,4,Cdaughter, 10, in Rowley Regis
OL,6,FThe defendant, wearing a grey jumper,
OL,7,Fattended the short hearing on Friday
OL,8,Fvia video-link and spoke only to
OL,9,Fconfirm her name and that she could
OL,10,Fhear Judge Michael Chambers KC.
OL,12,FShe appeared to be listening intently
OL,13,Fto proceedings, leaning forward so she
OL,14,Fcould hear what was being said.
OL,16,FJudge Chambers set a sentencing date
OL,17,Fof October 25 and said Kaur needed to
OL,18,Fbe produced in court for the hearing.
