OL,6,FAddressing Kaur, he said: "Your case
OL,7,Fis being adjourned for sentence,
OL,8,Flikely on the 25th of October. There
OL,9,Fwill be a need for further reports, so
OL,10,Fit is in your interests to co-operate
OL,11,Fwith the preparation of those reports."
OL,13,FIn a tribute released by her school
OL,14,Fafter her death, Shay was described as
OL,15,Fa "bright, happy, fun-loving child who
OL,16,Fwas well liked by all".
